snippet line
abbr 80 comment line
    `g:NeosnippetSnippets_CommentLine()`
    ${0}

snippet line_sub
abbr 80 sub comment line
options word
    `g:NeosnippetSnippets_SubCommentLine()`
    ${0}

snippet feature
options word
    feature${0}

snippet enhancement
options word
    enhancement${0}
